{{Infobox company | name = BE Semiconductor Industries N.V. | logo = Besi-semiconductor-logo.png | trading_name = Besi | type = [[Public company|Public]] | traded_as = BESI | founded = 1995 | founders = Richard Blickman (ceo since 1995) | industry = Semiconductors | hq_location_city = Duiven | hq_location_country = The Netherlands | area_served = Worldwide | website = https://besi.com }}
'''BE Semiconductor Industries N.V.''', simply called '''Besi''', is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] multinational company that designs and manufacturers [[semiconductor]] equipment.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/finance/stocks/companyProfile?rpc=66&symbol=BESIY.PK|title=Reuters Profile on Besi|last=|first=|date=|website=Reuters|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/quote/BESI:NA|title=BESI:EN Amsterdam Stock Quote - BE Semiconductor Industries NV|website=Bloomberg.com|access-date=2017-06-15}}</ref> The company was founded in May, 1995 by Richard Blickman, who still leads the company today. The company employees 1500 people, of which 200 are at its headquarters in [[Duiven]], a small town in the east of the Netherlands. It outsources production to its subsidiaries in China and Malaysia.
Besi is a publicly traded company, and its shares are listed on the Euronext Amsterdam stock market under the BESI ticker symbol.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.google.com/finance?q=AMS:BESI|title=BE Semiconductor Industries NV: AMS:BESI quotes & news - Google Finance|website=www.google.com|access-date=2017-06-15}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.euronext.com/nl/products/equities/NL0000339760-XAMS/quotes|title=BE SEMICONDUCTOR {{!}} Euronext|website=www.euronext.com|language=nl|access-date=2017-06-15}}</ref> In June, 2017, Besi was valued at around $2 billion.
